metadata.name: why am I dizzy
metadata.description:
Ming holding the stone table, looked at Lu Yao, but at this time, he found Lu Yao's face a little cold.



"Ha ha ha, Lu Ming, Yao Er to accompany you for three years, is nothing more than to nourish the pulse, now the time has come, your blood contribution?"



At this time, a middle-aged man appeared from the side, is Lu Yao's father.



Rumble!
